snippet.title: Amber Heard Faces 10 Years In Prison For *Secret* BRIBE!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Faces 10 Years In Prison For *Secret* BRIBE! 
Is Amber Heard really facing ten years in prison for a secret bribe? Find out in this video. I’m sure you’re well aware of the events that have surrounded Amber Heard and Johnny Depp so far. This seems to be one of those cases that do not appear to have an end, and the legal case just seems to move slowly in an unclear direction. No matter how little or how much you care, there is always someone that has your support in a case like this. For this one, it seems that Johnny has more public empathy than Amber Heard. What about you, though? Let me know in the comments.
